## Patch A: add input-type detection fallback regression

```powershell
Describe "GeometryNodesParser Priority 0 regressions" {
    BeforeAll {
        . "$PSScriptRoot/../module/LLMWorkflow/ingestion/parsers/GeometryNodesParser.ps1"
    }

    It "Does not throw when JSON-like input fails JSON probing during input-type detection" {
        $input = '{ this is not valid json but looks like it might be }'

        { Detect-GeometryNodesInputType -TextContent $input } | Should -Not -Throw
    }
}
```

## Patch B: add blend-text JSON fallback regression

```powershell
It "Falls back cleanly when JSON-style blend text fails Parse-GeometryNodesFromJson" {
    Mock Parse-GeometryNodesFromJson {
        throw 'json parse failed'
    }

    $text = '{ invalid json-ish geometry nodes text }'

    { Parse-GeometryNodesFromBlendText -TextContent $text } | Should -Not -Throw
}
```

